            <title><![CDATA[Questions linger over U.S.-Iran deal as details remain murky]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/questions-linger-over-u-s-iran-deal-as-details-remain-murky</link>
            <description><![CDATA[Meeting leaders of the top industrial nations at the G7 summit in the French Alps, President again extolled the framework deal the U.S. struck with Iran to start nuclear negotiations and end the war. But the prevailing question remains: What is actually in that deal? Days after it was announced, no text has been released publicly. White House correspondent Liz Landers reports.]]></description>
